# Development

- Copy .env.template to .env
- Create virtual environment
- Activate virtual environment
- Apply requirements file (pip install -r requirements.txt)
- Start dev server (PYTHONPATH=. python ./mm_tools/web/manage.py runserver)
- Start JS client (yarn start in mm_tools/client) if working on the client

# Deploying

- Build client with cli/build-client
- Check in to master to deploy to Heroku